 pay in cash.","mnemonic_en":null},{"spanish_text":"Tarjeta de crédito","english_text":"Credit card","section_name":"Daily Life","part_of_speech":"noun","definition_en":"A plastic or digital card issued by a financial institution that lets the holder borrow money to make purchases.","main_translations_es":["Tarjeta de crédito","Tarjeta bancaria","Tarjeta de pago"],"collocations":["apply for a credit card","credit card debt","credit card statement","credit card limit"],"example_sentence":"I need to apply for a new credit card for my online purchases.","example_es":"Necesito solicitar una nueva tarjeta de crédito para mis compras en línea.","example_en":"I need to apply for a new credit card for my online purchases.","mnemonic_en":null},{"spanish_text":"Cambio","english_text":"Change","section_name":"Daily Life","part_of_speech":"noun","definition_en":"the act or result of making something different; a transformation or alteration","main_translations_es":["Modificación","Alteración","Variación"],"collocations":["make a change","change of pace","change your mind","change the subject"],"example_sentence":"I need a career change.","example_es":"Necesito un cambio de carrera.","example_en":"I need a career change.","mnemonic_en":null},{"spanish_text":"Recibo","english_text":"Receipt","section_name":"Daily Life","part_of_speech":"noun","definition_en":"A written acknowledgment that something has been received, often confirming a payment.","main_translations_es":["Comprobante","Factura","Ticket"],"collocations":["receipt of payment","receipt number","receipt printer","receipt confirmation"],"example_sentence":"The receipt from the purchase is on the table.","example_es":"El recibo de la compra está sobre la mesa.","example_en":"The receipt from the purchase is on the table.","mnemonic_en":null},{"spanish_text":"Barato","english_text":"Cheap","section_name":"Daily Life","part_of_speech":"adjective","definition_en":"Low in price; inexpensive.","main_translations_es":["Económi