ially at work.","main_translations_es":["Jefe","Patrón","Superior"],"collocations":["the boss is coming","call the boss","boss level","boss around"],"example_sentence":"My boss gave me a raise last week.","example_es":"Mi jefe me dio un aumento la semana pasada.","example_en":"My boss gave me a raise last week.","mnemonic_en":null},{"spanish_text":"Clase","english_text":"Class","section_name":"Daily Life","part_of_speech":"noun","definition_en":"A group of students who are taught together, or a category of objects or ideas that share common characteristics.","main_translations_es":["Categoría","Tipo","Grupo"],"collocations":["class schedule","first class","classroom","class action"],"example_sentence":"The class is cancelled today.","example_es":"La clase está cancelada hoy.","example_en":"The class is cancelled today.","mnemonic_en":null},{"spanish_text":"Tarea","english_text":"Homework","section_name":"Daily Life","part_of_speech":"noun","definition_en":"School assignments given to be completed outside of class.","main_translations_es":["deber","trabajo","encargo"],"collocations":["do homework","homework assignment","homework help","homework deadline"],"example_sentence":"I have to finish my homework before dinner.","example_es":"Tengo que terminar mi tarea antes de la cena.","example_en":"I have to finish my homework before dinner.","mnemonic_en":null},{"spanish_text":"Estudiar","english_text":"Study","section_name":"Daily Life","part_of_speech":"verb","definition_en":"To devote time and attention to acquiring knowledge or skill in a subject.","main_translations_es":["Aprender","Repasar","Prepararse"],"collocations":["study hard","study abroad","study for the exam","study group"],"example_sentence":"I have to study for the exam.","example_es":"Tengo que estudiar para el examen.","example_en":"I have to study for the exam.","mnemonic_en":null},{"spanish_text":"Aprender","english_text":"Learn","section_name":"Daily Life","part_of_speech":"verb","definition_en":"To 