_en":"I like to have oat milk for breakfast.","mnemonic_en":null},{"spanish_text":"Bebida de soja","english_text":"Soy milk","section_name":"Cafe Counter Basics","part_of_speech":"noun","definition_en":"A plant-based beverage made from soybeans.","main_translations_es":["leche de soja","bebida vegetal de soja","leche vegetal de soja"],"collocations":["soy milk latte","add soy milk","drink soy milk","soy milk alternative"],"example_sentence":"I like soy milk at breakfast.","example_es":"Me gusta la bebida de soja en el desayuno.","example_en":"I like soy milk at breakfast.","mnemonic_en":null},{"spanish_text":"Refresco","english_text":"Soft drink","section_name":"Cafe Counter Basics","part_of_speech":"noun","definition_en":"A non-alcoholic, carbonated beverage.","main_translations_es":["bebida gaseosa","bebida refrescante","cola"],"collocations":["soft drink can","soft drink machine","soft drink industry","soft drink brand"],"example_sentence":"I bought a cold soft drink to go with the pizza.","example_es":"Me compré un refresco frío para acompañar la pizza.","example_en":"I bought a cold soft drink to go with the pizza.","mnemonic_en":null},{"spanish_text":"Limonada","english_text":"Lemonade","section_name":"Cafe Counter Basics","part_of_speech":"noun","definition_en":"A sweetened drink made from lemon juice, water, and sugar.","main_translations_es":["bebida de limón","refresco de limón","agua de limón"],"collocations":["lemonade stand","make lemonade","fresh lemonade","lemonade pitcher"],"example_sentence":"I like drinking fresh lemonade on hot days.","example_es":"Me gusta tomar limonada fresca en los días calurosos.","example_en":"I like drinking fresh lemonade on hot days.","mnemonic_en":null},{"spanish_text":"Batido","english_text":"Milkshake","section_name":"Cafe Counter Basics","part_of_speech":"noun","definition_en":"A cold, sweet beverage made by blending milk with ice cream or flavorings.","main_translations_es":["Malteada","Batido de leche"],"collocation