eferencia del pedido"],"collocations":["enter your order number","check the order number","order number is required","provide the order number"],"example_sentence":"Could you tell me your order number, please?","example_es":"¿Podrías decirme tu número de pedido, por favor?","example_en":"Could you tell me your order number, please?","mnemonic_en":null},{"spanish_text":"Recogida","english_text":"Pickup","section_name":"Cafe Counter Basics","part_of_speech":"noun","definition_en":"A vehicle with an open cargo area at the rear used for transporting goods.","main_translations_es":["Recolección","Recogimiento"],"collocations":["pick up the phone","pick up the tab","pick up where we left off","pick up speed"],"example_sentence":"The pickup of the package will be tomorrow at 10.","example_es":"La recogida del paquete será mañana a las 10.","example_en":"The pickup of the package will be tomorrow at 10.","mnemonic_en":null},{"spanish_text":"Reservado","english_text":"Reserved","section_name":"Cafe Counter Basics","part_of_speech":"adjective","definition_en":"Quiet and restrained; not inclined to share thoughts or feelings openly.","main_translations_es":["Guardado","Apartado","Retraído"],"collocations":["reserved seat","reserved table","reserved for","reserved parking"],"example_sentence":"The seat next to the window is reserved for first-class passengers.","example_es":"El asiento junto a la ventana está reservado para los pasajeros de primera clase.","example_en":"The seat next to the window is reserved for first-class passengers.","mnemonic_en":null},{"spanish_text":"Libre","english_text":"Free","section_name":"Cafe Counter Basics","part_of_speech":"adjective","definition_en":"Not costing any money; available without payment.","main_translations_es":["Desocupado","Sin costo","Disponible"],"collocations":["free of charge","free time","free will","free speech"],"example_sentence":"I am free to choose my own path.","example_es":"Soy libre de elegir mi propio camino.","examp