 and Society","part_of_speech":"noun","definition_en":"The process of combining separate parts into a unified whole.","main_translations_es":["Integración","Incorporación","Unificación"],"collocations":["system integration","cultural integration","integration testing","integration process"],"example_sentence":"The integration of the new employees into the company was very quick.","example_es":"La integración de los nuevos empleados en la empresa fue muy rápida.","example_en":"The integration of the new employees into the company was very quick.","mnemonic_en":null},{"spanish_text":"Discriminación","english_text":"Discrimination","section_name":"News and Society","part_of_speech":"noun","definition_en":"Unfair or prejudicial treatment of individuals or groups based on characteristics such as race, gender, age, or other attributes.","main_translations_es":["Segregación","Prejuicio","Exclusión"],"collocations":["racial discrimination","gender discrimination","discrimination lawsuit","discrimination policy"],"example_sentence":"Discrimination in the workplace is unacceptable.","example_es":"La discriminación en el lugar de trabajo es inaceptable.","example_en":"Discrimination in the workplace is unacceptable.","mnemonic_en":null},{"spanish_text":"Inclusión","english_text":"Inclusion","section_name":"News and Society","part_of_speech":"noun","definition_en":"The act or state of including someone or something, or the condition of being included.","main_translations_es":["Integración","Participación","Incorporación"],"collocations":["inclusion criteria","social inclusion","inclusion policy","inclusion in the classroom"],"example_sentence":"The inclusion of students with special needs in the classroom benefits all students.","example_es":"La inclusión de estudiantes con necesidades especiales en el aula beneficia a todos los alumnos.","example_en":"The inclusion of students with special needs in the classroom benefits all students.","mnemonic_en":null},{"spanish_text":"Acce